, \"from\": 247, \"to\": 285}, {\"ngram\": \"her statement performances\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 312}, {\"ngram\": \"the Summer Games\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a social media post on X (formerly Twitter), expressing gratitude the wrestler penned a heartfelt note dedicated to all the people who contributed towards her goal and were a part of her journey over the past few years.\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a social media post\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 367}, {\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 372}, {\"ngram\": \"formerly Twitter\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 390}, {\"ngram\": \"gratitude\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 413}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrestler\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 426}, {\"ngram\": \"a heartfelt note\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 450}, {\"ngram\": \"all the people\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"her goal\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 511}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"her journey\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 542}, {\"ngram\": \"the past few years\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She thanked her support team, including Dr Dinshaw Pardiwala, Dr Wayne Patrick Lombard, Coach Woller Akos, Physio Ashwini Jeevan Patil, Tajinder Kaur, Olympic Gold Quest team and Gagan Narang among others for their contributions.\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 639, \"end\": 646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patrick_Star\", \"score\": 0.9997355894129958, \"rank\": 0.00023511118181789438, \"text\": \"Patrick\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patrick_Star\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patrick_Star\"}, {\"begin\": 647, \"end\": 654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lombards\", \"score\": 0.981070935745598, \"rank\": 0.019149540656982877, \"text\": \"Lombard\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lombards\", \"dbpedia\"