r support team\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"Dr Dinshaw Pardiwala\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 628}, {\"ngram\": \"Coach Woller Akos\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"their contributions\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 796}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The letter begins with, \\\"Olympic rings: as a small girl from a small village I did not know what was the Olympics or what these rings meant.\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 939, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The letter\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 809}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic rings\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"a small girl\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"a small village\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 912}, {\"ngram\": \"these rings\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 932}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a small girl, I dream of things like long hair, flaunting a mobile phone in my hand and doing all these things that any young girl would normally dream of.\\\"\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 1099, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a small girl\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"long hair\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 989}, {\"ngram\": \"a mobile phone\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"my hand\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"all these things\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"any young girl\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The letter further notes, \\\"But survival taught me a lot.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The letter\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"survival\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Seeing my mother's hardships, never-give-up attitude and fighting spirit is what makes me the way I am.\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mother's hardships\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"never-give-up attitude\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"fighting spirit\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1230}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She taught me to fight for what is rightfully mine.\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When I think about courage I think about her and it is this courage that helps me fight every fight without thinking about the outcome.\\\"\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"courage\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"this courage\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"every fight\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"the outcome\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a triumphant victory in the semi-final 50 Kg women's freestyle wrestling match, Vinesh Phogat made it to the finals of the Olympic games but was disqualified for breaching weight criteria by 100 grams.\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1538, \"end\": 1551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a triumphant victory\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1478}, {\"ngram\": \"the semi-final 50 Kg women's freestyle wrestling match\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1536}, {\"ngram\": \"the finals\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1573}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic games\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1594}, {\"ngram\": \"weight criteria\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1645}, {\"ngram\": \"100 grams\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On August 7,she approached the Court of Arbitration for Sports to file a petition to grant her a silver medal, but on We